="Discover the microbiome&amp;rsquo;s role in diabetes&amp;nbsp;" loading="lazy"></picture></a></figure></section><section class="text flex flex-col"><header><a href="/a-question-of-balance-how-the-gut-microbiome-influences-diabetes-70525" target="_self"><div class="h3 max-2-lines l-h-3">A Question of Balance: How the Gut Microbiome Influences Diabetes</div></a></header><main><div class="displayAuthorAndTime"><span class="h6"><em>The Scientist</em> </span><span class="h6"></span><span class="h6"> | 1 min read</span></div><div class="max-2-lines l-h-3">The presence of beneficial or detrimental microbes pulls the host toward health or disease.</div></main><footer><div class="tabFooter flex flex-justify-end logo"><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/vendorNo/334/logo/47824/illumina-s.webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/vendorNo/334/logo/47824/illumina-s.png" type="image/png"><img src="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/vendorNo/334/logo/47824/illumina-s.png" alt="illumina" title="illumina" loading="lazy"></picture></div></footer></section></div><div class="ArticleSummary" data-aos="fade-up"><section class="thumbnail">  <figure class="thumbnailWrapper"><a href="/infographic-programmed-dna-elimination-71515" target="_self"><picture><source media="(min-width: 568px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71515/aImg/51614/article-12-23-issue-feature-dna-infog-t.webp" type="image/webp"><source media="(min-width: 568px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71515/aImg/51614/article-12-23-issue-feature-dna-infog-t.jpg" type="image/jpeg"><source media="(max-width: 400px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71515/aImg/51614/article-12-23-issue-feature-dna-infog-s.webp" type="image/webp"><source media="(max-width: 400px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71515/aImg/51614/article-12-23-issue-feature-dna-infog-s.jpg" type="image/jpeg"><so